# Desktop/Tablet Product Page for Laku Ecommerce

## OBJECTIVE
Create a comprehensive desktop and tablet product detail page at `/product/[id]` route optimized for larger screens (768px and above), using a SHEIN-inspired layout pattern.

## TARGET ROUTE
`http://localhost:3000/product/[id]`

## TARGET DEVICES
- Tablets: 768px - 1023px width
- Desktop: 1024px and above
- Landscape orientation
- Mouse/trackpad interactions

## DESIGN REFERENCE
Layout pattern inspired by SHEIN desktop interface:
- 60/40 split layout (image gallery left, product info right)
- Sticky right sidebar
- Vertical thumbnail strip
- Collapsible policy sections
- Multi-column product grids

## IMPORTANT DESIGN PHILOSOPHY
- **DO NOT specify exact colors** - Choose colors that match Laku brand, create excellent contrast, and follow modern ecommerce best practices
- **ADAPT, don't copy** - Use SHEIN's layout structure but maintain Laku identity
- Hover states for all interactive elements
- Smooth transitions and animations
- Generous whitespace and breathing room

---

## üíª DESKTOP/TABLET PAGE STRUCTURE

### LAYOUT INTEGRATION WITH EXISTING LAKU DESIGN

**CRITICAL - Use Your Existing Layout:**
- **DO NOT create new left sidebar** - Use your existing navigation sidebar with:
  - LAKU logo at top
  - Beranda (Home)
  - Video
  - Pesan (Messages)
  - Keranjang (Cart)
  - Profil (Profile)
  - Lainnya (More)
- **DO NOT create new header** - Use your existing search header
- Product page content goes in the MAIN CONTENT AREA (to the right of sidebar)

### 1. HEADER INTEGRATION (USE EXISTING)
Your existing header already has:
- Search bar: "Cari di LAKU..."
- Camera icon

**Add for Product Page Context:**
- Breadcrumb navigation (if space allows): Home > Category > Product
- Back button or browser back
- Share icon (if not already present)

**Keep these in your existing header component**

### 2. MAIN CONTENT CONTAINER
**This is the area to the RIGHT of your existing left sidebar:**

**Container Specifications:**
- **Width**: Fills remaining space after left sidebar (~85-90% of viewport)
- **Max-width**: 1400px (centered if very large screens)
- **Padding**: 24-40px horizontal, 20-32px top
- **Background**: White or your current background color
- **This area is scrollable** while left sidebar remains fixed

**Important**: 
- Don't overlap with your existing sidebar (LAKU logo + nav items)
- Content starts immediately to the right of sidebar
- Use your existing layout's spacing and padding conventions

---

## üìê TWO-COLUMN LAYOUT (PRIMARY STRUCTURE)

### LEFT COLUMN (60% width, 55-65% range)

#### A. IMAGE GALLERY SECTION

**Vertical Thumbnail Strip:**
- **Position**: Fixed on left side of image area
- **Width**: 80-100px
- **Thumbnails**:
  - Height: 80-100px each
  - Gap between: 8-12px
  - Border: 2px solid transparent (active gets accent color)
  - Hover: Slight scale (1.05), cursor pointer
  - Active: Bold border with accent color
- **Scrollable**: If more than 6-8 thumbnails
  - Scroll indicator arrows (top/bottom)
  - Mousewheel scroll when hovering
- **Layout**: Vertical flex column

**Main Product Image:**
- **Position**: Right of thumbnail strip
- **Size**: Fills remaining space (flexible)
- **Aspect ratio**: Maintained (typically 3:4 or 1:1)
- **Features**:
  - High resolution image
  - Zoom on hover (120-150% scale)
  - Click to open fullscreen gallery
  - Smooth transition when switching (300ms fade)
- **Overlays**:
  - Image counter badge (top-right): "1/4"
  - "Get The Look" button (over image, center-bottom if applicable)

**Full Gallery Container:**
- Display: flex
- Gap: 16-20px
- Total height: Auto based on aspect ratio

---

### RIGHT COLUMN (40% width, 35-45% range)

#### STICKY SIDEBAR BEHAVIOR
- **Position**: Sticky as user scrolls
- **Top offset**: Below fixed header (80-100px from top)
- **Stops sticking**: When reaching review section
- **Transition**: Smooth when becoming unstuck
- **Max height**: Viewport height minus header

#### B. PRODUCT INFORMATION (in sticky sidebar)

**Badges Row:**
- Horizontal flex
- Badges: "Trends", "Choice", featured seller badges
- Gap: 8px
- Small badges with icons

**Product Title:**
- Font size: 22-26px
- Font weight: 600-700
- Line clamp: 2-3 lines
- Color: Primary text
- Margin bottom: 12px

**SKU & Rating Row:**
- Small text (13-14px)
- SKU: "sku: sm2507119482691158.d #"
- Separator: "|"
- Star rating: Interactive stars
- Review count: Clickable link (scrolls to reviews)
- "109+ Reviews" format

**Price Section:**
- Current price: 32-38px, bold, accent color
- Original price: 20-22px, strike-through, gray
- Discount badge: Pill, "-50%" format
- Payment info text: "Pay now in 4 payments of $4.00..." with info icon

**Bestseller Badge** (if applicable):
- "#2 Bestseller in Casual - Basic Men Sweatpants"
- With category icon
- Clickable to category
- Arrow icon on right

#### C. VARIANT SELECTION (in sidebar)

**Color Selector:**
- Label: "Color: [Selected Color]"
- "Large Image" link on same line (right-aligned)
- Color options: Horizontal flex wrap
- Each swatch:
  - Size: 56-64px square or circle
  - Border: 2px solid (active gets bold accent border)
  - Image thumbnail if color has pattern
  - Hover: Slight scale, cursor pointer
  - Gap: 8-12px

**Size Selector:**
- Label: "Size [US Size]" with size system dropdown
- Size buttons: Grid (4-5 columns)
- Each button:
  - Height: 44-48px
  - Min width: 80-100px
  - Border: 2px solid
  - Selected: Filled background + bold border
  - Out of stock: Opacity 0.5, diagonal line
  - Hover: Border color change
  - Text: Size + (US equivalent)
- Gap: 8px

**Size Helper Links:**
- "Size Guide" with icon (opens modal)
- "Check My Size" with icon (interactive tool)

**Quantity Selector:**
- Label: "Quantity"
- Layout: Horizontal
- Minus button | Number input | Plus button
- Styled buttons with borders
- Width: 120-140px total

#### D. ACTION BUTTONS (in sidebar)

**Add to Cart Button:**
- Width: 80-85% of sidebar
- Height: 50-54px
- Background: Black or primary brand color
- Text: "ADD TO CART"
- Font: Bold, 16-17px, uppercase
- Icon: Shopping bag (optional)
- Hover: Slight color darken, subtle scale
- Click: Loading state (spinner)

**Wishlist Button:**
- Width: 15-20% of sidebar
- Height: 50-54px
- Icon: Heart outline (filled when saved)
- Border: 2px solid
- Hover: Fill with light color
- Position: Right of cart button

**Points/Rewards Info:**
- Small text below buttons
- "Earn up to 16 SHEIN Points calculated at checkout"
- Icon + text

#### E. COLLAPSIBLE INFO SECTIONS (in sidebar)

Each section has:
- Header row: Icon + Title + Chevron (down/up)
- Collapsed by default (except first)
- Click to expand/collapse
- Smooth height transition (300ms)
- Border between sections

**1. Shipping to [Country]:**
- Icon: Truck
- Expanded content:
  - Free Shipping badge (or cost)
  - Estimated delivery: "Jan 27 - Feb 3"
  - Additional details
  - Shipping provider info

**2. Return Policy:**
- Icon: Return arrow
- Expanded content:
  - "Free Return" text
  - Return window: "7 business days"
  - Terms link

**3. Shopping Security:**
- Icon: Shield
- Expanded content:
  - Safe Payments (checkmark)
  - Privacy Protection (checkmark)
  - Additional security info

**4. Sourced from [Seller Name]:**
- Icon: Store
- Expanded content:
  - "Sold by and Ships from SHEIN"
  - "To report this seller and/or product" link
  - Seller rating/info

#### F. ADDITIONAL INFO SECTIONS (in sidebar, below collapsibles)

**Description (expandable):**
- "Description" header with chevron
- Product tags: "Trends", "#ChicFWEdi", "Winter (<10/60)"
- Expand to show full description

**Size & Fit (expandable):**
- "Size & Fit" header with chevron
- Expand to show measurements and fit guide

**About Store (expandable):**
- "About Store" header with chevron
- Seller card when expanded:
  - Seller logo + name + "Choice" badge
  - Rating (4.90) + items count + followers
  - User browsing indicator
  - "All Items" button
  - "+ Follow" button

#### G. MATCHING STYLES (in sidebar)

**Section Title**: "Matching Styles"
**Minimize/Collapse option**: Dash icon

**Grid Layout**:
- 2-3 columns
- Multiple categories:
  - "You May Like" (10 items)
  - "You May Love" (3 items)
  - "More Style" (1 item)
  - "Sets" (1 item)
  - "You May Also Like" (15 items)

**Each Category Card**:
- Product images in grid
- Item count overlay
- Hover: Slight elevation
- Click: Navigate to product or gallery

