## üé® DESKTOP VISUAL DESIGN

### DESIGN CONSISTENCY WITH LAKU
**Critical**: Match your existing Laku design system

**Your Current Design Patterns:**
- **Sidebar Background**: Light gray or white (from screenshot)
- **Main Content Background**: White
- **Price Color**: Red - prominent for current/sale price
- **Original Price**: Gray, struck through, smaller
- **Sold Count**: Gray text, "X+ terjual" format
- **Product Cards**: White, rounded corners, subtle shadow
- **Product Images**: Rounded corners, clean presentation
- **Search Bar**: Rounded, light background with placeholder text
- **Icons**: Simple, minimal line icons
- **Spacing**: Clean, generous whitespace between elements

**Product Page Must Match:**
- Same color palette (especially red for prices)
- Same typography and font weights
- Same border radius values
- Same shadow styles
- Same spacing scale
- Button styles consistent with existing UI
- Navigation item styling when applicable

### Typography
- Product title: 22-26px, bold
- Price: 32-38px, bold
- Body text: 15-16px
- Small text: 13-14px
- Button text: 16px, semi-bold

### Spacing
- Container padding: 24-40px
- Section spacing: 40-60px vertical
- Card padding: 20-24px
- Column gap: 24-32px

### Hover States
- Buttons: Color darken, subtle scale (1.02)
- Links: Color change, underline
- Images: Slight zoom, cursor pointer
- Cards: Elevation increase (shadow)
- Thumbnails: Border color, scale (1.05)

### Borders & Shadows
- Cards: shadow-sm or border 1px
- Elevated elements: shadow-md
- Active elements: Accent color border
- Border radius: 8-12px

### Transitions
- Duration: 200-300ms
- Easing: ease or ease-in-out
- Properties: transform, opacity, color, box-shadow

---

## üîß DESKTOP FUNCTIONALITY

### Image Gallery
- Thumbnail click: Change main image, smooth fade
- Main image hover: Zoom in place (cursor: zoom-in)
- Main image click: Open fullscreen lightbox
- Arrow keys: Navigate images
- Thumbnail strip scroll: Mousewheel when hovering

### Sticky Sidebar
- Stick on scroll: When user scrolls past hero
- Stop sticking: When reaching reviews section
- Calculate height: Adjust based on content
- Smooth transition: No jarring jumps

### Collapsible Sections
- Click header: Toggle expand/collapse
- Smooth animation: Height transition 300ms
- Chevron rotation: 180deg when expanded
- Preserve other sections: Only one expands at a time (accordion) OR all can expand (independent)

### Variant Selection
- Size/color button click: Select, update state
- Out of stock: Cannot select, tooltip on hover
- Hover effects: Border color change
- Size guide modal: Open on click, overlay background

### Add to Cart
- Click: Validate selections
- Loading: Button shows spinner
- Success: Toast notification, cart badge updates
- Error: Show error message if validation fails

### Reviews
- Filter/sort: Update display
- Tag filters: Toggle active, refetch
- Pagination: Navigate pages
- Helpful button: Increment count, disable after click
- Review images: Click to open gallery

### Product Cards (Customers Also Viewed)
- Hover: Show wishlist and quick cart
- Quick cart: Add to cart without leaving page
- Wishlist: Toggle saved state
- Click card: Navigate to product
- Image hover: Zoom effect

