## üéØ RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS

### Tablet (768px - 1023px)
- Two-column layout begins
- Smaller font sizes than desktop
- Right sidebar: 45% width
- Product grid: 3 columns
- Reduced padding/margins

### Small Desktop (1024px - 1279px)
- Full two-column layout
- Right sidebar: 40% width
- Product grid: 3-4 columns
- Standard spacing

### Medium Desktop (1280px - 1599px)
- Optimal layout proportions
- Right sidebar: 38-40% width
- Product grid: 4-5 columns
- Comfortable spacing

### Large Desktop (1600px+)
- Max-width container (1600px)
- Centered content
- Product grid: 5 columns
- Generous spacing

