## ‚ö° DESKTOP PERFORMANCE

- Lazy load images below fold
- Optimize image sizes (800-1200px for main, 100px for thumbnails)
- Prefetch on hover (product cards)
- Code splitting by section
- Smooth 60fps animations
- Initial load < 2s on broadband

