## üé® COLOR SCHEME GUIDANCE

Choose colors that:
- Match Laku brand identity
- Create clear visual hierarchy
- Make CTAs prominent (cart button especially)
- Work well for badges (Trends, Choice, Bestseller)
- Provide excellent hover state feedback
- Ensure collapsible section headers are clear
- Make selected states obvious (size, color)
- Support trust elements (shipping, security badges)
- Create good contrast for sidebar on white page

**Desktop Considerations:**
- Sidebar background might differ slightly from main content
- Active states need to be more subtle (no touch feedback)
- Hover states should be clear but not jarring
- Focus indicators for keyboard navigation

