**DELIVERABLE:**
A complete desktop/tablet product page (768px+) using SHEIN's proven layout pattern with a sticky sidebar, vertical image gallery, collapsible sections, and multi-column product grids, all adapted to maintain Laku's brand identity.

**NOTE:** This is Part 2 of 2. Mobile view (320-767px) is a separate implementation with different layout and interaction patterns.